# Planner Pro — Implementation Plan

Based on [implementation.prompt.md](file:///c:/Github/app/implementation.prompt.md), covering the full existing codebase analysis.

---

## Current Architecture Summary

| Layer | Key Files |
|---|---|
| **Auth** | [AuthManager.kt](file:///c:/Github/app/app/src/main/java/com/example/auth/AuthManager.kt), [AuthViewModel.kt](file:///c:/Github/app/app/src/main/java/com/example/auth/AuthViewModel.kt) — Firebase Auth + Google Sign-In |
| **Data (Local)** | [AppDatabase.kt](file:///c:/Github/app/app/src/main/java/com/example/data/local/AppDatabase.kt) — Room DB v5 with `tasks`, `notes`, `categories`, `subtasks` tables |
| **Data (Remote)** | [FirestoreDataSource.kt](file:///c:/Github/app/app/src/main/java/com/example/data/network/FirestoreDataSource.kt) — Skeleton only, unused |
| **Calendar** | [CalendarRepository.kt](file:///c:/Github/app/app/src/main/java/com/example/data/repository/CalendarRepository.kt), [CalendarSyncViewModel.kt](file:///c:/Github/app/app/src/main/java/com/example/calendar/CalendarSyncViewModel.kt) — Google Calendar REST API |
| **UI** | [MainActivity.kt](file:///c:/Github/app/app/src/main/java/com/example/MainActivity.kt) (~2439 lines), [OtherScreens.kt](file:///c:/Github/app/app/src/main/java/com/example/OtherScreens.kt) (~1752 lines), [PlanScreen.kt](file:///c:/Github/app/app/src/main/java/com/example/PlanScreen.kt) |
| **Notifications** | [NotificationHelper.kt](file:///c:/Github/app/app/src/main/java/com/example/notification/NotificationHelper.kt), [PlanNotificationManager.kt](file:///c:/Github/app/app/src/main/java/com/example/notification/PlanNotificationManager.kt) |
| **Settings** | [SettingsViewModel.kt](file:///c:/Github/app/app/src/main/java/com/example/settings/SettingsViewModel.kt), [UserPreferencesRepository.kt](file:///c:/Github/app/app/src/main/java/com/example/settings/UserPreferencesRepository.kt) — DataStore |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The local Room database currently has **no user association** — all data is global on the device. This is the root cause of bug #1.

## Resolved Decisions

| Question | Answer |
|---|---|
| Guest mode | **Removed.** Users must sign in. No offline guest access. |
| Data migration | **Destructive.** Fresh DB (version 6), no migration of old data. |
| Presets | Full snapshot: all plans + subtasks + today's tasks. Date-independent template applied to any day. |
| "Trainers" | Actually means **alarm clock management** — creating/managing morning alarms from the app. |
| Smart band | **Xiaomi Smart Band 9 Pro** — notification mirroring via Mi Fitness. |
| Markdown | Full Markdown rendering + keep quick task `[ ] ` creation shortcut. |
| Note widget | Opens notes page with empty note + shows today's notes list. |
| Export | Standard Android share sheet. |
| XP values | Task = 10 XP, note = 5 XP, streak = 20 XP, plan = 5 XP. |
| App icon | Minimalistic, stylish, Indigo-branded. |
| Priority | Phase 1→2→4→3→6→5→7→8 |

