### 1.2 Logout → redirect to login

**Problem:** `onSignOut` callback exists but only calls `settingsViewModel.signOut(onSignOut)`. The auth state is not observed at the top level to force navigation when it becomes `Idle`.

#### [MODIFY] [MainActivity.kt](file:///c:/Github/app/app/src/main/java/com/example/MainActivity.kt) — `MainAppNavigation`
- Add a `LaunchedEffect` that observes `authViewModel.authState` — when it transitions to `Idle`, navigate to `"login"` and pop the entire backstack
- **Remove** the guest-mode "Continue Offline" button entirely
- Prevent navigation to `"main"` route without authentication

